  "title": "Project Administrator",
  "description": "<p>Job scope:</p><ul><li>Assisting on administrative role</li><li>Data entry (MS Word, Excel, Powerpoint & ERP)</li><li>Prepare worker namelist and submission to landlord</li><li>Support project scheduling, meeting minutes and coordination tasks</li><li>Perform other administrative duties as assigned</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>ITE / Diploma or equivalent </li><li>Project management or related field</li><li>Keen eye for details and ability to priorities work independently</li><li>Meticulous and fast pace</li><li>Good personality, hardworking, willing to learn, organized, responsible</li><li>Good communication skills and ability to work with different teams</li><li>Able to work in a fast-paced environment </li><li>Familiarity with construction or engineering terms (added advantage, not required)</li><li>Ideally available to start work on short notice</li></ul>",
